ng innovation and digital transformation for supply chain development. The development of taskoriented and open science policies to utilize new technologies is crucial for the economic restructuring of modern society.'], r.t_start = null, r.edge_row = 187;
MATCH (s:KGEntity {id: 'policies'}), (t:KGEntity {id: 'supply_chain_environment_complexity'})
