ndustry j at time t . Manulab jt = 2010 is the median number of employees in all companies in industry j in 2010 (base year). The ratio of firm i \' s employee share in industry j \' s production sector in 2010 (base year) to the median share of all companies in industry j \' s production  sector  in  2010  (base  year)  is  represented as Labor ijt = 2010 Manulab jt = 2010 .  The independent variable Robot in Equation (1) is expressed using the natural logarithm of the firm\'s robot penetration, i.e., Robot = log ( RobotFP ) .'], r.t_start = null, r.edge_row = 230;
